main event: A UFO was reported in Brownfield, Texas on September 23, 1965, observed for 8 minutes.
interesting points: The object was reported as stationary during the observation,There was physical evidence associated with the sighting,The observation was made from a back yard,The object appeared bright and then faded on a cycle,The witness was a reliable civilian vice president.
witness description: Mr. Miley, Age 32, Vice President, J & Ethyle Distributing Company
